HEADWORD: Terpinol
<hw>Ter"pin*ol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Terpin</ets>
+ L. <ets>ol</ets>eum oil.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Any oil
